[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       1239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       1240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - *Disparity-calculation method.* Absolute difference between highest and lowest cohort, computed per-metric per-cycle. The disparity is not the variance; it is the max-minus-min across cohorts, which surfaces the worst-case disparity that the review committee needs to investigate.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+       1241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - *Per-metric emission cadence.* Match rate: weekly. False-acceptance rate: weekly. Response-time aging (per-cohort p50/p95): weekly. Sampled error rate (from the review queue's resolved cases): monthly.
